70 (D) In the absence of an approved report, the cochairpersons may file with the Clerk
71 of the House of Representatives and the Secretary of the Senate copies of the minutes
72 of the meetings of the committee in lieu thereof.
73 (7) Abolishment. The committee shall stand abolished on December 1, 2025.
